sub_title: CEO Heart for Health Group - Cardiologie Centra Nederland (CCN) is member of Heart for Health Group
summary:
Experienced Board member / CEO with a demonstrated history of working in the Healthcare/ Service/ Consultants and Event-industry. With a mindset which is always focussed on accelerating for value creation, growth, innovation, digital, technology and sustainability. 

Strong entrepreneurship and professional graduated from Singularity University, Insead and university of Amsterdam (drs.) and University of Rotterdam (post-doc).
